Tomcat Installation :

$ sudo yum list | grep java-1.8.0

$ sudo yum install java-1.8.0-openjdk -y

$ java -version

$ cd /opt/

$ sudo wget http://apachemirror.wuchna.com/tomcat/tomcat-8/v8.5.45/bin/apache-tomcat-8.5.45.tar.gz

$ sudo tar xf apache-tomcat-8.5.45.tar.gz

$ sudo rm apache-tomcat-8.5.45.tar.gz
 
$ sudo mv apache-tomcat-8.5.45/ tomcat8

$ sudo chown -R ec2-user:ec2-user tomcat8/

$ cd tomcat8/bin

To Start the Tomcat Service

$ ./startup.sh

To Stop the Tomcat Service

$ ./shutdown.sh


